    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;In the footage&quot; is an exploration-based horror adventure.</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281040/extras/da3f00a855ba19eb428603c6075d3dff.avif?t=1685235609\" width=600 height=700 /></span><br><br>Awakening in an empty room, you begin by playing a videotape left on the floor, pondering the meaning of the footage displayed. At this point, you have nothing else to do. It's only natural.<br><br>Who are you?<br>Why are you here?<br>What is this place?<br>What should you do?<br>Is it acceptable to do that?<br>Or is it no longer a matter of good or evil?<br><br>The dolls have noticed you.<br>They will come to understand what is happening and attempt to stop it.<br>You don't have much time.<br><br>Look at the clock.<br>You must get out of that small room.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An exploration-based horror adventure.<br></li><li> You awaken in a small room and need to understand the situation and find a solution.<br></li><li> By playing the videotape, you can explore and observe the scenes within the footage.</li></ul>",
